abstract_ssm: The Faculty Minutes contain meeting minutes and related documents to Polytechnic faculty meetings.  The minutes reflect the name changes of the institution from the Polytechnic Institute of Brooklyn (PIB) to the Polytechnic Institute of New York (PINY) to Polytechnic University, and, finally, to the Polytechnic Institute of New York University.
corpname_ssm: Poly Archives at the Bern Dibner Library of Science and Technology, NYU Libraries
